title: AH LORD GOD!
verses: Ah Lord God! Thou hast made the heaven=And the earth by thy great power=Ah Lord God! Thou hast made the heaven=And the earth by thy stretched out arm,
chorus: Nothing is too difficult for thee:=Nothing is too difficult for thee:=Great and mighty God=Great in counsel mighty in deeds, mighty in deeds=Nothing, nothing, absolutely nothing=Nothing is too difficult for thee.
